(44, 159, 'JA Simpli Features', 'ja-simpli-features', '<p>JoomlArt is excited to announce that we are going to release JA Simpli this April (planned on Mid of April). Simpli is truly Free Joomla template and probably will be the best free Joomla templates as other templates in our Free Joomla template series: T3 Blank, Purity I, Purity II and Purity III. JA Simpli is clean and light without any framework, it is fast, responsive ande easy to customize based on well strutured codebase and intuitive admin panel.</p>', '\r\n\r\n<h4>Core features:</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul class="ja-checklist">\r\n<li>No Framework</li>\r\n<li>Fully responsive</li>\r\n<li>Multiple premade layouts: Default, Magazine, Corporate and Landing page</li>\r\n<li>Live theme editor</li>\r\n<li>Integrates Bootstrap 2, Font Awesome 4</li>\r\n<li>Intuitive admin panel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Let\'s check some screenshots of the template, we will continuously update more to the blog post to keep you posted with the template development process.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>4 premade layouts for Business, Coporate, Magazines and Landing page</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The template is some kind of based template so it should be clean and simple and can be adapted for multipurposes. The demo is more about building layout and to give you better starting point when making your own site.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>1. Default layout</h4>\r\n\r\n<div class="img-caption" style="margin-bottom:10px"><img alt="free joomla template" src="//joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/blog/2016/ja-simpli/layout1-resize.jpg" itemprop="image">\r\n<p>JA Simpli Default layout</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align="center"><a title="free joomla template" target="_blank" href="//joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/blog/2016/ja-simpli/layout1-fullsize.jpg">View full screenshot →</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>2. Magazine Layout</h4>\r\n\r\n<div class="img-caption" style="margin-bottom:10px"><img alt="magazine layout" src="//joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/blog/2016/ja-simpli/layout2-resize.jpg" itemprop="image">\r\n<p>JA Simpli Magazine layout</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align="center"><a title="magazine layout" target="_blank" href="//joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/blog/2016/ja-simpli/layout2-fullsize.jpg">View full screenshot →</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>3. Coporate Layout</h4>\r\n\r\n<div class="img-caption" style="margin-bottom:10px"><img alt="magazine layout" src="//joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/blog/2016/ja-simpli/layout3-resize.jpg" itemprop="image">\r\n<p>JA Simpli Coporate layout</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align="center"><a title="corporate layout" target="_blank" href="//joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/blog/2016/ja-simpli/layout3-fullsize.jpg">View full screenshot →</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>4. Landing Page Layout - Onepage layout</h4>\r\n\r\n<div class="img-caption" style="margin-bottom:10px"><img alt="magazine layout" src="//joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/blog/2016/ja-simpli/layout4-resize.jpg" itemprop="image">\r\n<p>JA Simpli Landing Page layout - Onepage layout</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p align="center"><a title="Landing Page layout - Onepage layout" target="_blank" href="//joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/blog/2016/ja-simpli/layout4-fullsize.jpg">View full screenshot →</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Customize style for almost elements of the site in real time</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class="img-caption" style="margin-bottom:10px"><img alt="easy to customize joomla template" src="//joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/blog/2016/ja-simpli/live-theme-editor.jpg" itemprop="image">\r\n<p>Ease of customization Joomla template</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>This is truly magic tool to customize style based on pre-defined parameters. You can change font-family, font size, color, logo and so many other things, once you make changes, it is shown in preview window instantly.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Manage positions with ease</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class="img-caption" style="margin-bottom:10px"><img alt="manage position" src="//joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/blog/2016/ja-simpli/layout-configuration.jpg" itemprop="image">\r\n<p>Position Configuration Panel</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Managing layout with ease based on the intuitive layout configuration panel with lots of options built-in. You can make the layout full-width or boxed style, enable/disable the main content, configure the right and left column.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Adding scripts via Custom Code panel</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class="img-caption" style="margin-bottom:10px"><img alt="manage position" src="//joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/blog/2016/ja-simpli/custome-code.jpg" itemprop="image">\r\n<p>Adding scripts with ease </p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Instead of looking for coresponding files to add scripts (like Google Analytics) to, you just need to paste the scripts to the fields in the custom code panel.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="ja-checklist">\r\n	<li>After head: scripts will be added after the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag.</li>\r\n	<li>Before head: scripts will be added before the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag.</li>\r\n	<li>After body: scripts will be added after the <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> tag.</li>\r\n	<li>Before body: scripts will be added before the <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> tag.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>New web technologies & optimized code base</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The template is built with new web technologies: LESS, Bootstrap 2, Font awesome 4. The codebase is clean and well structured to make the site lighweght and perform well. The customization is easy with intuitive workflow for modifying style, override layouts ... The well structured files/folder system makes it easy for user to find the corresponding files to modify.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="alert alert-info">The template is still in development process so those features are not finalized, there can be changes but for sure, we are working hard to make it as good as possible with more cool features.</p>', 1, 18, '2020-12-02 06:47:48', 42, '', '2020-12-02 06:47:48', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2020-12-02 06:47:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image